":188540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a4dc5251a555d143c95c848bb62a7f9a1fc6036","tid":1253482,"uid":10451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"幫你推俾姑姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:46:46.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d9971c1962a1e6653fe0554d3ac495a6728fa1","tid":1253482,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:47:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6e269a486d1118b9f2bbca68fa2e7da070d9a3f","tid":1253482,"uid":188540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"76d3ecfd414067b5b05af4b7390808ff180d20af","tid":1253482,"uid":188540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a4dc5251a555d143c95c848bb62a7f9a1fc6036","tid":1253482,"uid":10451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"幫你推俾姑姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:46:46.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:51:09.000Z","msg":"未打完就send咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排好多post提大家登記做選民，但如果無一個公平嘅選舉無論我哋有幾多票都係無用。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9deacf4dd0de509b8ad7912a6da1bbd75cc14a4","tid":1253482,"uid":127108,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:53:20.000Z","msg":"過兒 姑姑聽到了 練完功再幫你"},{"pid":"953b0c501fa56e7cbd6b9065a53a995064c1fd94","tid":1253482,"uid":149420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:09:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>G20前行動討論</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n個人認為現時最重要係︰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1）香港人再嚟一次(或持續)大型遊行或者和平野餐</span></span>，時間點唔可以係7月1日，必須係G20當天及G20之前 (6月28日之前)，向侵侵同歐洲各國正式表態（唔能夠只靠Liberate Hong Kong嘅白宮聯署╴因為可以做數，一定唔及遊行人數嘅公信力），向佢地表達香港人要d乜，等佢地拎嚟同中共傾。我地唔只係要「徹回」，我地係要「Liberate Hong Kong」、「我要真普選／Universal Suffrage Now」。因為只有「真普選」，先可以徹底解決「再強推送中」、「警權」等等問題。所有現時嘅訴求，必須升級到更高層次&mdash;「真普選」上面。美國幫到你今次徹回送中又點？一日港共政權仲係度，惡法重有機會死灰復燃，要求林鄭下台就更無謂，下個上台都係港共嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅集會同上兩次集會嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">意義係唔同</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好以為上兩次遊行出咗嚟今次就可以唔出</span></span>，請大家繼續努力！<br />\n<br />\n目前行動一覽︰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">a. 民陣6.26有搞集會</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/G20-37_IznKq_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FG20-37_IznKq_1200x0.png&h=70903166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">b. 6.26野餐</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/czpKAyw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczpKAyw.jpg&h=db733117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">c. 626行動！去G20各國領事館請願！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1251726/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1251726/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2）繼續推高Liberate Hong Kong 白宮聯署數</span></span>，現在已過10萬，暫時以20萬做目標！聯署連結︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1ytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=1694af9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記得簽完要email confirm</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3) 幫手推po﹗將此post的原帖推上熱門！</span></span>依家唔討論行動好快就到G20﹗原帖連結︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1252876/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1252876/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n4）搵人整「Liberate Hong Kong」、「我要真普選／Universal Suffrage Now」牌到時派比人集會用<br />\n<br />\n5）Forward 上面嘅訊息／圖片比身邊朋友知，搵更多更多人去集會，並且明白提升訴求層次至普選層面嘅重要性！今次嘅集會同上兩次集會嘅意義係唔同，唔好以為上兩次出左今次可以唔出，請大家繼續努力！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請合力做到以上五點，就算你去唔到各方嘅集會，都幫幫手做第2、第3點</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份G20相關討論︰<br />\n<br />\nG20戰線：解放香港白宮聯署20萬目標<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1252188/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1252188/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">G20前不要與港共對話</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1252478/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1252478/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[G20] 集資登美日德公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1252527/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1252527/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n楊衛隆：g20 一戰定江山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1246699/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1246699/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[G20緊急]最大公約數有兩個1.liberate Hong Kong 2.香港落實普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1243416/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1243416/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"13a2e581574f5e0f97c50b7c9810b8efb96c9751","tid":1253482,"uid":13490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:28:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0d1f82e3c7924e16f30f9a64a8faba75343fb70","tid":1253482,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"